				</p>

				<p class="copyright_text">
					<a href="mailto:info@knowhow.de" target="_new">info@knowhow.de</a><br/>
					<a href="https://www.knowhow.de" target="_new">www.knowhow.de</a>
				</p>

			</div>

			<div style="clear: both;">

				<p class="copyright_version_text"><span id="copyright_version_span"></span></p>

			</div>

		</div>

	</body>

</html>